    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total dream! This beauty is in absolutely immaculate condition\u2014honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been pampered since day one, kept spotless, and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
