    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines showroom quality. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and shows absolutely no signs of wear, tear, or aging. The exterior boasts a flawless factory finish, enhanced by a professional ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like shine and protection. There are zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections on the bodywork. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free of any creases or bolster wear, and the interior still retains its original new-car aroma. Every technological feature, from the infotainment system to the advanced driver assistance suite, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a full, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is as clean as the day it was manufactured. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or a discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle in impeccable, untouched condition. I welcome and encourage independent professional inspections to verify its pristine state.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional provenance, maintained to a concours-level standard. This specimen exhibits an impeccable exterior finish and a pristine interior environment, entirely free from even the most negligible signs of wear. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically unrivaled, it represents the definitive choice for the discerning collector seeking an uncompromising driving experience.",
