    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system for razor-sharp throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced as a preventative measure. The suspension retains its factory-correct geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the precise lateral dynamics the M-division is known for. With zero deferred maintenance and an immaculate undercarriage, this M3 offers a pure, analog driving experience for the discerning collector.",
